 279:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_uart.c ****   Depending on the frame length defined by the M1 and M0 bits (7-bit,
 280:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_uart.c ****   8-bit or 9-bit), the possible UART formats are listed in the
 281:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_uart.c ****   following table.
 282:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_uart.c **** 
 283:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_uart.c ****   Table 1. UART frame format.
 284:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_uart.c ****     +-----------------------------------------------------------------------+
 285:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_uart.c ****     |  M1 bit |  M0 bit |  PCE bit  |             UART frame                |
 286:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_uart.c ****     |---------|---------|-----------|---------------------------------------|
 287:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_uart.c ****     |    0    |    0    |    0      |    | SB |    8 bit data   | STB |     |
 288:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_uart.c ****     |---------|---------|-----------|---------------------------------------|
 289:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_uart.c ****     |    0    |    0    |    1      |    | SB | 7 bit data | PB | STB |     |
 290:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_uart.c ****     |---------|---------|-----------|---------------------------------------|
 291:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_uart.c ****     |    0    |    1    |    0      |    | SB |    9 bit data   | STB |     |
 292:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_uart.c ****     |---------|---------|-----------|---------------------------------------|
 293:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_uart.c ****     |    0    |    1    |    1      |    | SB | 8 bit data | PB | STB |     |
 294:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_uart.c ****     |---------|---------|-----------|---------------------------------------|
 295:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_uart.c ****     |    1    |    0    |    0      |    | SB |    7 bit data   | STB |     |
 296:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_uart.c ****     |---------|---------|-----------|---------------------------------------|
 297:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_uart.c ****     |    1    |    0    |    1      |    | SB | 6 bit data | PB | STB |     |
 298:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_uart.c ****     +-----------------------------------------------------------------------+
